Add `python-json-logger` to requirements. Configure in `main.py` lifespan.

## SLO Definition

For this service (teaching tool, non-critical):

| SLO | Target |
|-----|--------|
| Availability | 99.5% (43 min/month downtime budget) |
| `/generate` latency (p95) | < 30s (LLM calls are slow — set realistic expectations) |
| `/status` latency (p99) | < 200ms |
| Error rate | < 1% of requests |

